getDefaultSize

protected Dimension getDefaultSize()
Return the default size of an empty display area of the combo box using the current renderer and font. This method was overridden to use SynthComboBoxRenderer instead of DefaultListCellRenderer as the default renderer when calculating the size of the combo box. This is used in the case of the combo not having any data.

Overrides:
getDefaultSize in class BasicComboBoxUI
Returns:
the size of an empty display area
